text: Colubraria latericium is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Colubrariidae. ==Description== The length of the shell attains 60.6 mm. ==Distribution== This marine species occurs off Madagascar. ==References== * Bozzetti, L., 2008. Colubraria latericium (Gastropoda: Hypsogastropoda: Buccinidae: Pisaniinae) nuova specie dal Madagascar. Malacologia Mostra Mondiale 61: 17-18 ==External links== * Category:Colubrariidae Category:Gastropods described in 2008
title: Colubraria latericium
